        {
            "id": "action",
            "instance": "6eea692a-7e33-4cb7-bbd2-380580b52a89",
            "properties": [
                [
                    "name",
                    "Valid Accounts"
                ],
                [
                    "ttp",
                    [
                        [
                            "tactic",
                            "TA0001"
                        ],
                        [
                            "technique",
                            "T1078"
                        ]
                    ]
                ],
                [
                    "description",
                    "In The Matrix acquires valid credentials — spanning local administrator, domain, and generic user accounts — from stealer malware logs, credential markets, and prior breach datasets. The actor's extensive reliance on legitimate credentials across all three account sub-types reflects a broad credential acquisition operation, enabling access to a wide range of victim environments without triggering brute-force or anomaly detection controls."
                ],
                [
                    "confidence",
                    null
                ],
